metadata.description:
Entre Nosotros is a track in collaboration with Bulla Beatz and Alana Lazaro, two artist from Cúcuta Colombia. We recorded this song 3 years ago on 24H Studios.

After being on the creative camp on Medellin the next stop was Cúcuta, the birth city of Bulla Beatz; the creator of the instrumental and the connection with Alana Lazaro.

This song is a combination of latin cultures.
We hope you like it!

Performed by Alex Paul and Alana
Produced by Bulla Beatz
